# Vite proxies /api/auth/* to auth-service (5001) and everything else under
# /api/* to project-service (5002) in dev — see vite.config.js. No env vars
# are needed locally.
#
# In production, the two services are on different hosts (e.g. Render), so
# you need either a gateway/reverse proxy in front of both, or platform-level
# rewrites (e.g. Vercel rewrites) routing /api/auth/* and /api/* separately.
# See the root README's "Deployment" section for the exact setup.
